  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `v2022.07.03`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\nWhen running `make docker-compose` the script now expects `sudo` permissions which should not be needed.\r\n\r\n```\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon systemd[1]: Started erigon.service.\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: Docker build args:\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]:     DOCKER_UID: 1014\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]:     DOCKER_GID: 1014\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: Ensuring host OS user exists with specified UID/GID...\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: ✔️ host OS user exists: erigon\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: mkdir -p /home/erigon/.local/share/erigon /home/erigon/.local/share/erigon-grafana /home/erigon/.local/share/erigon-prometheus\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: ls -aln /home/erigon/.local/share | grep -E \"472.*0.*erigon-grafana\" || sudo chown -R 472:0 /home/erigon/.local/share/erigon-grafana\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: We trust you have received the usual lecture from the local System\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: Administrator. It usually boils down to these three things:\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]:     #1) Respect the privacy of others.\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]:     #2) Think before you type.\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]:     #3) With great power comes great responsibility.\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: sudo: no tty present and no askpass program specified\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon erigon[14231]: make: *** [Makefile:76: setup_xdg_data_home] Error 1\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon systemd[1]: erigon.service: Main process exited, code=exited, status=2/INVALIDARGUMENT\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon systemd[1]: erigon.service: Failed with result 'exit-code'.\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon systemd[1]: erigon.service: Service RestartSec=100ms expired, scheduling restart.\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon systemd[1]: erigon.service: Scheduled restart job, restart counter is at 4.\r\nJul 25 02:01:27 erigon systemd[1]: Stopped erigon.service.\r\n```\r\n",
